{"tid":1825421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人將警員資料上傳群組 警方將為警員索取創傷報告","createTime":"2020-01-15T09:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T09:37:30.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"73ae0c3faf4ccaf08e2bf33a24d25724941fb896","tid":1825421,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"一名電訊公司職員被指將警員及親友個人資料上傳至 Telegram 群組，被控串謀披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料等罪及目的在於使其本人或他人不誠實地獲益而取用電腦兩罪，案件今（20 日）於九龍城裁判法院再提訊，控方指已索取法律意見，案件將會轉介區院處理，案件押後下月 25 日再訊。控方又指基於案件性質及警員事主的意願及利益等，申請禁止報導令並將警員的身份改為中國籍男子陳某，並禁止傳媒報導任何可以識別其身份的資料，獲署理主任裁判官嚴舜儀批准。警方又將會為事主索取創傷報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%8A%E5%82%B3%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E8%87%B3telegram%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E7%94%B3%E4%BB%A4%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD-%E5%B0%87%E7%82%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B4%A2%E5%89%B5%E5%82%B7%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%2587%25B3telegram%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=8c9bf967\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B3%2587%25E